      "desc_zh": "通过你在这台设备上配置的 Google OAuth 应用管理 Google 日历事件。",
      "desc_en": "Manage Google Calendar events through a Google OAuth app configured on this device.",
      "icon": null,
      "category": "productivity",
      "os": [
        "darwin",
        "linux",
        "win32"
      ],
      "skill_version": "0.1.3",
      "requires": {
        "bins": [
          "node"
        ],
        "env": [
          {
            "name": "GOOGLE_ACCESS_TOKEN",
            "source": "host",
            "help_text": "Short-lived Google access token injected by Sanqian after Google account connection. Do not ask users to paste refresh tokens or client secrets here.",
            "help_url": "https://developers.google.com/calendar/api/guides/auth"
          }
        ]
      },
      "install": [],
      "is_preinstalled": false,
      "package_url": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/yushaw/sanqian-releases@main/config/skill-curated/dist/google-calendar/google-calendar-0.1.3.zip",
      "package_sha256": "8b183f620cbb7ef81f5655e3222d5bcc95277cbfaf68c91fc9678450d4367ee6",
      "package_size": 3258,
      "auth": {
        "mode": "oauth2",
        "kind": "generic_oauth2",
        "profile_id": "oauth2.google.calendar-events",
        "provider": "google",
        "brokered": true,
        "env_names": [],
        "runtime_env_names": [
          "GOOGLE_ACCESS_TOKEN"
        ],
        "required_scopes": [
          "https://www.googleapis.com/auth/calendar.events"
        ],
        "notes": [],
        "host_setup": {
          "required": true,
          "owner": "host",
          "end_user_flow": "connect_account_only",
          "required_provider_config_keys": [
            "client_id",
            "client_secret"
          ],
          "fields": [
            {
              "name": "client_id",
              "scope": "provider",
              "type": "text",
              "required": true,
              "secret": false,
              "help_text": "Google OAuth client ID for the OAuth app you configure on this device.",
              "help_url": "https://developers.google.com/identity/protocols/oauth2/web-server"
            },
            {
              "name": "client_secret",
              "scope": "provider",
              "type": "password",
              "required": true,
              "secret": true,
              "help_text": "Google OAuth client secret from the OAuth app you configure on this device.",
              "help_url": "https://developers.google.com/identity/protocols/oauth2/web-server"
            }
          ],
          "notes": [
            {
              "zh": "先创建或选择你自己的 Google Cloud 项目，然后在 Google Auth Platform 里配置 OAuth consent screen。",
              "en": "Create or select your own Google Cloud project, then configure the OAuth consent screen under Google Auth Platform."
            },
            {
              "zh": "如果你要用 Google Tasks，先在当前项目里启用 Google Tasks API；如果你要用 Google Calendar，先启用 Google Calendar API。否则连接成功后第一次调用通常会直接报 403 / SERVICE_DISABLED。",
              "en": "If you want to use Google Tasks, enable the Google Tasks API in the current project first; if you want to use Google Calendar, enable the Google Calendar API first. Otherwise the first API call after connecting usually fails with 403 / SERVICE_DISABLED."
            },
            {
              "zh": "创建一个类型为 Web application 的 OAuth Client ID。",
              "en": "Create an OAuth Client ID of type 'Web application'."
            },
            {
              "zh": "把 https://auth.sanqian.ai/skills/auth/callback 加到授权回调地址里，然后把这个应用的 client_id 和 client_secret 填在下方。",
              "en": "Add https://auth.sanqian.ai/skills/auth/callback as an authorized redirect URI, then paste that app's client_id and client_secret in the fields below."
            },
            {
              "zh": "如果这个 OAuth 应用还处于测试模式，把你准备连接的 Google 账号加入 test users。",
              "en": "If the OAuth app is still in testing mode, add the Google account you plan to connect as a test user."
            },
            {
              "zh": "测试中的未验证应用通常会看到 Google 的风险提示页。确认这是你自己创建的应用后，点击 Advanced，再继续进入该应用完成授权即可。",
              "en": "Unverified apps in testing usually show Google's warning page. After confirming this is the OAuth app you created, click Advanced and continue to the app to finish authorization."
            }
          ]
        }
      }
